settings.helper_text:
One channel handle per line. Format: @handle, @handle=BaseNumber, or @handle=BaseNumber:TitleFilter

Examples:
@NASA=92
@RyanHallYall=90
@VirtualRailfan=91:Horseshoe|La Grange

All currently live streams for each handle are detected. Title filter is a case-insensitive regex. Channels without =Number are auto-assigned from Starting Channel Number.
